front.title: •Insignificant Rebellion (V)
front.gametext: If Ralltiir Operations on table, deploy on table. Forfeit values are not modified by Do They Have A Code Clearance?. Once per battle, when you draw battle destiny, may exchange a card in hand with a card of same card type in Lost Pile. (Immune to Alter.)
front.lore: 'Your fleet is lost. And your friends on the Endor moon will not survive. There is no escape, my young apprentice.'
